166
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:42,633
<i>Why London?</i>
Tom's renovating
a house.

167
00:16:42,635 --> 00:16:45,803
<i>My grandmother
passed a few years ago</i>

168
00:16:45,805 --> 00:16:50,375
