the family house,
so I thought I'd fix it up.

169
00:16:50,377 --> 00:16:54,212
Good for you.

170
00:16:54,214 --> 00:16:57,648
So, Mrs. Wright,
how are you, um,
how are you liking London?

171
00:16:57,650 --> 00:16:59,751
Anna, please.

172
00:16:59,753 --> 00:17:03,421
