isn't one for giving up.

178
00:17:20,407 --> 00:17:22,840
[Laughing]

179
00:17:26,111 --> 00:17:27,745
Anyhow...

180
00:17:27,747 --> 00:17:29,914
So, thank you for the tea.

181
00:17:32,618 --> 00:17:34,519
<i>It was very good.</i>

182
00:17:36,455 --> 00:17:39,157
